<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's become an established name in the fashion world, after soaring to fame as the 'Posh' member of the Spice Girls.</p>

<p>And Victoria Beckham served as her own best advert for her eponymous clothing line on Friday, when she shared footage of herself modelling one of her designs.</p>

<p>The singer-turned-designer, 46, took to her Instagram Stories to share a brief clip of herself strutting in high fashion style as she donned a bold floral dress.</p>

<p>Model: Victoria Beckham served as her own best advert for her eponymous clothing line on Friday, when she shared footage of herself modelling one of her designs</p>

<p>The stylish gown featured a high neckline and pleating at the form-flattering skirt, which was cinched at the waist with a matching sash belt.</p>

<p>With her chestnut brown tresses falling to her shoulders in lustrous waves, the mother-of-four wore a light palette of makeup with a dewy finish.</p>

<p>Taking to her main Instagram grid, the star shared a post of herself posing in different angles, along with the caption: 'Details of one of the beautiful printed pieces in the #VBPAW20 collection x vb.'</p>

<p>Chic: The singer-turned-designer, 46, took to her Instagram Stories to share a brief clip of herself strutting in high fashion style as she donned a bold floral dress</p>

<p>Cinched: The stylish gown featured a high neckline and pleating at the form-flattering skirt, which was cinched at the waist with a matching sash belt</p>

<p>Pics: Taking to her main Instagram grid, she shared a post of herself posing in different angles</p>

<p>The posts come after Victoria's husband David, who is reportedly being lined up for a stint on Celebrity Bake Off, is said to have been experimenting with recipes during the COVID-19 lockdown.</p>

<p>According to reports, Victoria 'couldn't get enough' of David's homemade pizza after using various different toppings.</p>

<p>Although it has been claimed that the fashion designer who is known for her love of steamed fish and vegetables, is 'back to clean eating' now autumn is approaching. </p>

<p>A source told The Sun: 'Victoria hasn't touched a carb since 2001. But at the start of lockdown, David started experimenting with recipes — making the dough from scratch and trying various toppings.'</p>

<p>Beloved daughter: She is often seen posing up a storm with her nine-year-old daughter Harper</p>

<p>Sons: Victoria and husband David are also parents to Brooklyn, 21, Romeo, 18, and Cruz, 15</p>

<p>Added the source: 'Victoria eventually relented and had a small slice.    </p>

<p>'Things progressed and, basically, she couldn't get enough of David's delicious golden dough balls.' </p>

<p>MailOnline has contacted the Beckham's representative for comment.  </p>

<p>David has been perfecting his recipes on their lavish Cotswold estate where he has been spent the COVID-10 lockdown with his wife and three children, Romeo, 18, Cruz, 15, and daughter Harper, nine.</p>

<p>Their eldest son Brooklyn, 21, spent it in America with fiancée Nicola Peltz. </p>

